{"tid":581564,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"打完你右面，一定打埋你左面! Coffee Lake可完美在 100/200 系列主機板運行","createTime":"2018-03-05T12:32:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-13T13:06:30.000Z","uid":67384,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"203d75122e8fa9fcd4a095fd5bfbd86c8f75868e","tid":581564,"uid":67384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T12:32:25.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: left;\">轉自HKEPC<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkepc.com/16421\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkepc.com%2F16421&d=WlnnxHFi7%2F5XORf1i7aNZDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=6e137f22\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkepc.com/16421</a><br />\n文: Cherry Kwok / <br />\n<br />\nIntel 第八代 Core &ldquo;Coffee Lake&rdquo;處理器即使採用 LGA1151 插槽，但必需要配搭 300 系列晶片組的主機板使用，讓不少用家對新處理器都甚有微言，最新在外國媒體 <a href=\"http://Overclock.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FOverclock.net&d=WlnnxHFi7%2F5XORf1i7aNZDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=2c485d08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Overclock.net</a> 的網站討論區中再有玩家分享了成功在 100/200 系列主機板上使用到 &ldquo;Coffee Lake&rdquo; 處理器，並成功在多款不同的 100/200 系列主機板上成功運行 Core i3-8100 處理器，同時還找到了解決幾個穩定性及兼容性問題的方法。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nIntel 刻意在 &ldquo;Coffee Lake&rdquo; 桌面版處理器全線增加了核心數量，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">並以電氣特性變化的為理由</span></span></strong>，即使在保持採用 LGA1151 接口的情況下，亦要用家<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>搭配幾乎毫無變化的 300 系列晶片組</strong></span></span>，首發的亦只有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>昂貴的 Z370</strong></span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n其實，ASUS 在 Coffee Lake&rdquo;處理器推出不久後亦曾經忍不住披露第八代 Core 原本是兼容 100/200 系主機板，但是 Intel 最後關頭改變了主意。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nCoffee Lake<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://Overclock.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FOverclock.net&d=WlnnxHFi7%2F5XORf1i7aNZDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=2c485d08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Overclock.net</a> 網站討論區中的幾位玩家 rootuser123、LittleHill、dsanke、elisw、Mov AX、0xDEAD 終於徹底揭開了這一謎題，事實證明，&ldquo;Coffee Lake&rdquo; 與基於 200 系列及 100 系列晶片組的舊款 LGA1151 主機板是兼容的。幾位玩家發現，Intel 使用軟件通過 CPU 微碼、iGPU UEFI GOP 驅動程式以及 ME 管理引擎特定框架等等，以便識別新的處理器晶片組，同時阻止 Coffee Lake 能夠在較舊的主機板上運行。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n經過反複測試，Core i3-8100 已經可以在 H110、B150、Q170、Z170、B250、Z270 等主機板上完美運行，日常操作無問題，也可以順利通過各種軟件檢測和測試，而且無論 iGPU 還是獨立繪圖卡都毫無障礙。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>原文有破解指南</em></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </div>"},{"pid":"0c89126b0c8582cfa2a127df912fb30d8dec6994","tid":581564,"uid":61259,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T12:37:10.000Z","msg":"煙條真係仆街廠黎"},{"pid":"d66b2f0e442679ec6aa60e673a148e14465316bd","tid":581564,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T12:55:00.000Z","msg":"既然煙屌咁撚賤,咁一撚定要抵制返幾年唔買新Intel CPU/底板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"789b179785d237dfc92c1be704daa79cca935c4f","tid":581564,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T12:55:31.000Z","msg":"行到6c6t/6c12t先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋4c4t只有資格做i3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85c0a323f0d3c14d2947011b835815da2ad635be","tid":581564,"uid":1518,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T13:02:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>買Intel正ON9</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"bca89d633eba2de2b7df47fe9fe8945790882dca","tid":581564,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T13:10:40.000Z","msg":"AMD萬歲"},{"pid":"34ea0f33ade319